description: ‚ÄúI‚Äôm gonna show you what the real Elvis is like tonight.‚Äù Don‚Äôt miss Austin Butler and Tom Hanks in THE film of the summer. See Baz Luhrmann‚Äôs #ElvisMovie only in theaters June 24. ‚ö°Ô∏è #TCB https://elvis.warnerbros.com https://www.facebook.com/ElvisMovie https://www.instagram.com/ElvisMovie https://twitter.com/ElvisMovie ELVIS is an epic, big-screen spectacle from Warner Bros. Pictures and visionary, Oscar-nominated filmmaker Baz Luhrmann that explores the life and music of Elvis Presley, starring Austin Butler and Oscar winner Tom Hanks. A thoroughly cinematic drama, Elvis‚Äôs (Butler) story is seen through the prism of his complicated relationship with his enigmatic manager, Colonel Tom Parker (Hanks). As told by Parker, the film delves into the complex dynamic between the two spanning over 20 years, from Presley‚Äôs rise to fame to his unprecedented stardom, against the backdrop of the evolving cultural landscape and loss of innocence in America. Central to that journey is one of the significant and influential people in Elvis‚Äôs life, Priscilla Presley (Olivia DeJonge). Starring alongside Butler and Hanks, award-winning theatre actress Helen Thomson (‚ÄúTop of the Lake: China Girl,‚Äù ‚ÄúRake‚Äù) plays Elvis‚Äôs mother, Gladys, Richard Roxburgh (‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù ‚ÄúBreath,‚Äù ‚ÄúHacksaw Ridge‚Äù) portrays Elvis‚Äôs father, Vernon, and DeJonge (‚ÄúThe Visit,‚Äù ‚ÄúStray Dolls‚Äù) plays Priscilla. Luke Bracey (‚ÄúHacksaw Ridge,‚Äù ‚ÄúPoint Break‚Äù) plays Jerry Schilling, Natasha Bassett (‚ÄúHail, Caesar!‚Äù) plays Dixie Locke, David Wenham (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings‚Äù Trilogy, ‚ÄúLion,‚Äù ‚Äú300‚Äù) plays Hank Snow, Kelvin Harrison Jr. (‚ÄúThe Trial of the Chicago 7,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe High Note‚Äù) plays B.B. King, Xavier Samuel (‚ÄúAdore,‚Äù ‚ÄúLove & Friendship,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Twilight Saga: Eclipse‚Äù) plays Scotty Moore, and Kodi Smit-McPhee (‚ÄúThe Power of the Dog‚Äù) plays Jimmie Rodgers Snow. Also in the cast, Dacre Montgomery (‚ÄúStranger Things,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Broken Heart Gallery‚Äù) plays TV director Steve Binder, alongside Australian actors Leon Ford (‚ÄúGallipoli,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Pacific‚Äù) as Tom Diskin, Kate Mulvany (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúHunters‚Äù) as Marion Keisker, Gareth Davies (‚ÄúPeter Rabbit,‚Äù ‚ÄúHunters‚Äù) as Bones Howe, Charles Grounds (‚ÄúCrazy Rich Asians,‚Äù ‚ÄúCamp‚Äù) as Billy Smith, Josh McConville (‚ÄúFantasy Island‚Äù) as Sam Phillips, and Adam Dunn (‚ÄúHome and Away‚Äù) as Bill Black. To play additional iconic musical artists in the film, Luhrmann cast singer/songwriter Yola as Sister Rosetta Tharpe, model Alton Mason as Little Richard, Austin, Texas native Gary Clark Jr. as Arthur Crudup, and artist Shonka Dukureh as Willie Mae ‚ÄúBig Mama‚Äù Thornton. Oscar nominee Luhrmann (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù) directed from a screenplay by Baz Luhrmann & Sam Bromell and Baz Luhrmann & Craig Pearce and Jeremy Doner, story by Baz Luhrmann and Jeremy Doner. The film‚Äôs producers are Luhrmann, Oscar winner Catherine Martin (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù), Gail Berman, Patrick McCormick and Schuyler Weiss. Toby Emmerich, Courtenay Valenti and Kevin McCormick executive produced. The director‚Äôs behind-the-scenes creative team includes director of photography Mandy Walker (‚ÄúMulan,‚Äù ‚ÄúAustralia‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer and costume designer Catherine Martin (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù), production designer Karen Murphy (‚ÄúA Star Is Born‚Äù), editors Matt Villa (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúAustralia‚Äù) and Jonathan Redmond (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù), Oscar-nominated visual effects supervisor Thomas Wood (‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù), music supervisor Anton Monsted (‚ÄúAustralia,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù) and composer Elliott Wheeler (‚ÄúThe Get Down‚Äù). Principal photography on ‚ÄúElvis‚Äù took place in Queensland, Australia with the support of the Queensland Government, Screen Queensland, and the Australian Government‚Äôs Producer Offset program. A Warner Bros. Pictures Presentation, A Bazmark Production, A Jackal Group Production, A Baz Luhrmann Film, ‚ÄúElvis‚Äù will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to release in theaters in North America on June 24, 2022, and internationally beginning 22 June 2022.

title: Dennis Chambers Hears Tool For The First Time
tags: dennis chambers|dennis chambers drum solo|dennis chambers in the pocket|danny carey|drum lesson|pearl drums|dennis chambers zildjian live|dennis chambers tool|dennis chambers 2022|dennis chambers drumeo|tool schism|tool progressive rock|danny carey live|larnell lewis enter sandman|fun with drums|drum video|Dennis Chambers Hears Tool For The First Time|dennis chambers fatback groove|drumeo|drumeo learning song by ear
description: What if funk/fusion drummer Dennis Chambers was the drummer for Tool? (Don‚Äôt tell Danny Carey.)Dennis is known for his legendary backbeat and funky style. So of course we felt mischievous and we dared him to try playing ‚ÄúSchism‚Äù, one of Tool‚Äôs biggest songs. It‚Äôs full of odd time signatures, quick, complex changes and unexpected accents, and Dennis had never heard it before.But we didn‚Äôt ask him to learn the real drum parts: we wanted to see what he‚Äôd come up with on his own after hearing the song once. While you‚Äôll hear the song with drums in this video, Dennis was actually listening to a drumless track.‚ÄúThis is not me,‚Äù he warned us as he listened through the track, but ‚Äúin my younger days, this would‚Äôve been up my alley!‚ÄùHow will Dennis Chambers not only learn a song he‚Äôs never heard before, but in a style he‚Äôs unfamiliar with ‚Äì and in odd time, at that?Since the song doesn‚Äôt have a drum track, he listens for two things: the style and the time signature. Watch Dennis‚Äô playthrough where he gives it his own spin. It‚Äôs solid, it‚Äôs groovy, and there‚Äôs some unexpected footwork later on. It‚Äôs amazing how much a song can change with a different approach on the drums.You‚Äôve never heard Schism played like this before!If you like Dennis Chambers, he has an entire 12-lesson course on funk drumming for Drumeo members. title: Riding Berm Peak at Night was more difficult and foolish than I thought
tags: backyard|mountain biking|cycling|outdoors|mountain bikes|enduro|mtb|mtb jumps|mtb stunts
description: This has been a long time coming. Anyone who watches this channel knows I love night riding, but until now I have never attempted to ride Berm Peak at night. This is due to a variety of reasons, most of which should be pretty obvious. Bike lights are designed for singletrack‚Äînot wallrides and whale tails. Tonight, we throw caution to the wind and give it a shot on my backyard mountain bike trails.Also tonight, we‚Äôll test out some new lights from Outbound Lighting. I met the owner of the company at Sedona Mountain Bike Festival, holding down the booth all by himself. Tom is not only an entrepreneur, but an engineer, so we can be sure Outbound‚Äôs marketing department isn‚Äôt getting in the way of the important stuff. These lights were remarkably simple, free of gimmicks, very well thought out, and very bright. They also turn on and off with simple taps of the power button instead of confounding combinations that so many other manufacturers insist on. Best of all, they‚Äôre really fairly priced for what you‚Äôre getting. So I‚Äôm going to run these long term and see how they work out!Trail Evo (flood light) https://www.outboundlighting.com/products/trail-evo-bike-lightHangover (spot light) https://www.outboundlighting.com/products/hangover-bike-helmet-lightBerm Peak Hoodies, Beanies, Jerseys, Shirtshttps://cognativemtb.com/collections/seths-bike-hacks-collectionWant us to review your unique mountain bike or outdoor product? https://www.sethsbikehacks.com/product-review/Check out our main channel https://youtube.com/c/sethsbikehacksFollow me on Instagram https://instagram.com/sethsbikehacksBerm Peak Merch https://cognativemtb.com/collections/seths-bike-hacks-collectionInstagram https://www.instagram.com/sethsbikehacksFacebook https://www.facebook.com/sethsbikehacksMusic in this video is from http://share.epidemicsound.com/trQSgand https://soundstripe.com?fpr=seth20Join my Patreon and 100% of the proceeds go towards projects in the mountain biking community. description: Hey guys! Today I am trying to tackle the HUGE challenge of drawing ALL my characters into ONE artwork. I ended up doing this digitally using procreate. This was SO time consuming, but I had a ton of fun bringing back all of my original characters in this massive digital painting.I also put this design onto shirts and a poster on my store! Check it out!SHIRT: https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/listing/jam-packed-bunch-design?product=46POSTER: https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/listing/jam-packed-bunch-art-print?product=624ME NAILS: https://slateland.com/collections/menails___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh üòÇ ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 27 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating, painting and general art videos here. description: Today‚Äôs Roblox In a Nutshell will be on Bee Swarm Simulator.Roblox Bee Swarm simulator is a classic Roblox simulator game where you walk around with your bees to collect pollen and honey so you can get better equipment to get pollen and honey faster.Like all the other Roblox simulator games, the objective is to get STRONG and RICH. To get from noob to pro, the player needs to buy more bees, improve their bee hive, buy better equipment, complete quests, kill mobs, complete challenges, and use codes to get some items. The better stuff the player gets, the more honey and pollen they will gather. The game is very grindy, just like all other simulators, and most people would use macros or scripts to farm.There are 45 types of bees, and they all have different stats and abilities. Since the maximum number of bees a player can have is 50, they need to find the best hive build (combination of bees) to get honey fast. Rarer bees are usually higher on the tier list, and some, like the windy bee, are hard to obtain.On top of bees, people need to grind for equipment and items like Tide Popper, Dark Scythe, Gummyballer, translator, and The Planter Of Plenty to farm more efficiently. They let the player gather more pollen, unlock new quests and drop better stuff.This video will show you everything there is to the game. It is not a complete guide, but there are some tips you can follow to get more honey. Like always, this video is filled with a crap ton of dead memes in the form of funny moments/montages. Bee Swarm Simulator used to have events like the Christmas 2021 event with snowflakes and gingerbread bears, but since then, there has been no update. I hope you enjoyed this Bee Swarm Simulator video. Meet friendly bears, complete their quests and get rewards! As your hive grows larger and larger, you can explore further up the mountain. Use your bees to defeat dangerous bugs and monsters. Look for treasures hidden around the map. Discover new types of bees, all with their own traits and personalities!What is ROBLOX? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet¬≠to¬≠be¬≠dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúROBUX‚Äù).
